    <title>使用Mongo語法做資料查詢</title>
    <link href="https://akoncc.github.io/2020/05/16/use-mongo-syntax-to-query/"/>
    <id>https://akoncc.github.io/2020/05/16/use-mongo-syntax-to-query/</id>
    <published>2020-05-16T03:37:01.812Z</published>
    <updated>2020-05-16T03:37:01.812Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近常常遇到要查詢 mongo 內資料的情境<br>來持續做個紀錄<span class="text-nowrap"><i class="fa fa-pencil fa-fw"></i><span class="text-nowrap"><i class="fa fa-pencil fa-fw"></i><span class="text-nowrap"><i class="fa fa-pencil fa-fw"></i>，免得又忘了 </p><h2 id="單一-Key-Value-查詢"><a href="#單一-Key-Value-查詢" class="headerlink" title="單一 Key:Value 查詢"></a>單一 Key:Value 查詢</h2><hr><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">db.getCollection(<span class="string">'CollectionName'</span>).find(&#123;<span class="symbol">Key:</span>QueryValue&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果是型別是 <code>string</code> 記得要在 Value 加上雙引號<br>如果是 <code>null</code>，可以直接下 <code>null</code> 來查詢</p><h2 id="比較值查詢"><a href="#比較值查詢" class="headerlink" title="比較值查詢"></a>比較值查詢</h2><hr><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">db.getCollection(<span class="string">'CollectionName'</span>).find(&#123;<span class="symbol">Key:</span>&#123;$ne<span class="symbol">:QueryValue</span>&#125;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>$ne:</code> 不等於<br><code>$eq:</code> 等於<br><code>$gte:</code> 大於等於<br><code>$lte:</code> 小於等於</p><h2 id="多重條件查詢"><a href="#多重條件查詢" class="headerlink" title="多重條件查詢"></a>多重條件查詢</h2><hr><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">db.getCollection(<span class="string">'CollectionName'</span>).find(&#123;<span class="symbol">Key:</span>&#123;$ne<span class="symbol">:QueryValue</span>&#125;, <span class="symbol">Key:</span>&#123;$in<span class="symbol">:</span>[<span class="number">123</span>, <span class="number">456</span>]&#125;&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>$in:</code> 同 SQL 的 IN，可包含多個同型別的條件</p><h2 id="查詢的型別為-Array"><a href="#查詢的型別為-Array" class="headerlink" title="查詢的型別為 Array"></a>查詢的型別為 Array</h2><hr><figure class="highlight rb"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">db.getCollection(<span class="string">'CollectionName'</span>).find(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="symbol">Key:</span>&#123;$in<span class="symbol">:</span>[<span class="number">123</span>, <span class="number">456</span>]&#125;, </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="symbol">ArrayKey:</span>&#123;$elemMatch<span class="symbol">:</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="symbol">Key:</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            $lte<span class="symbol">:Value1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            $gte<span class="symbol">:Value2</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>$elemMatch:</code> 找出跟條件相同的資料，裡面可以放入比較值的查詢</p>]]></content>
    
