    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>紀錄一下目前有安裝且有在使用的套件 ~</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">分類</th><th align="center">套件名</th><th align="left">用途</th><th align="left">安裝網址</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">通用</td><td align="center">Chinese (Traditional) Language Pack for Visual Studio Code</td><td align="left">繁中化</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=MS-CEINTL.vscode-language-pack-zh-hant" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketplace</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Golang</td><td align="center">Go</td><td align="left">編譯 golang</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ms-vscode.Go" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketplace</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Docker</td><td align="center">Docker</td><td align="left">可撰寫 Dockerfile</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ms-azuretools.vscode-docker" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketplace</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Json</td><td align="center">Paste JSON as Code</td><td align="left">將 json 格式轉為 class</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=quicktype.quicktype" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketplace</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">通用</td><td align="center">Beautify</td><td align="left">針對部份的程式語言排版</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=HookyQR.beautify" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketplace</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Markdown</td><td align="center">markdownlint</td><td align="left">類似 SonarLint，會讓 md 更好閱讀</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=DavidAnson.vscode-markdownlint" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketplace</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Markdown</td><td align="center">Markdown All in One</td><td align="left">主要針對排版</td><td align="left"><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=yzh